result.name: Yvonne's Noodles

reviews.text: They’re making food with heart, and really care to feed us a good meal!

Edit : 2nd time there. I took a soup for 43 hkd. It was big and the taste was good. 

I took one of the cheapest option and it tasted good. 30 hkd for Noodle with sesame paste, peanuts, some spices and 2 leaves of lettuce. The portion was quite big
not bad, heavy taste
Pretty good Chongqing noodle place in Hung Hom. Quality has slightly declined since it first opened, but there still isn't anything in the same category to compare with in Hong Kong.
The ladies making the noodles are really nice. And food is good too.

result.name: 一碗小麵

reviews.text: They’re making food with heart, and really care to feed us a good meal!

一直都覺得呢度的豆花涼拌米線非常出色，今日再食，落單個阿姐打單就豆花涼拌豆線，黎左碗湯仲熱到出煙，我都算，比錢果刻我話你比碗熱嘅普通米線仲老屈我食果碗係涼拌米線，收多我十蚊..........==

都唔了解下比左咩客人，錢你識收。
都好食都好，我唔會再幫襯囉
好一般 唔係唔好食
味道濃，油份較多，畔麪前菜不錯
川味麵館，一般水平，位小地窄，風味麻麻
